Kenapa kamu tidak mengangkat telepon?

33
00:03:03,159 --> 00:03:04,999
Aku sedang bekerja.

34
00:03:05,300 --> 00:03:07,830
Periksa kotak pesanmu. Bekerja apa?

35
00:03:08,400 --> 00:03:09,400
Astaga.

36
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,800
Periksalah kotak pesanmu.

37
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:15,640
Uhm Cho Rong pergi menangkap Kim Moo Young.

38
00:03:16,510 --> 00:03:18,010
Mereka datang.

39
00:03:18,010 --> 00:03:20,779
- Mereka datang!
- Cepat!

40
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,520
Tersangka datang!

41
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:42,499
- Jawab pertanyaanku!
- Tunggu sebentar!

42
